<h3>Pingry COVID-19 Update</h3>
<h5>A change has been noted on your student's isolation status.</h5>
<hr/>

<p>Dear Parent/Guardian of <%= "#{@student.first_name} #{@student.last_name}"%>,</p>

<p>According to Pingry's records, <%= @student.first_name%> is currently in an isolation period after receiving a potentially positive, presumed positive, or confirmed positive diagnosis for COVID-19. Thank you for your recent update on <%= @student.first_name%>’s isolation status.</p>

<p>Please note that <%= @student.first_name%> will only be permitted to return to campus once all documentation from your child's physician has been updated in the Magnus Health Portal (Coronavirus - COVID-19 Clearance), their "Overall Status" field reads "Isolation Complete," and you receive a call from one of our school nurses approving <%= @student.first_name%>'s return to campus. If there are any additional updates to <%= @student.first_name%>’s isolation status, please contact <a href="mailto:contacttracing@pingry.org">contacttracing@pingry.org</a>.</p>

<p>Thank you for your partnership as we work to keep Pingry safe!</p>

Your Child's Current Isolation Status: 
<ul>
    <li>Start Date: <%= @isolation.start_isolation %></li>
    <li>Date of Symptom Improvement: <%= @isolation.date_improving || "Not Yet Improving" %></li>
    <% if @isolation.confirmed %>
        <li><%= "Confirmed Positive" %></li>
    <% elsif @isolation.potential %>
        <li><%= "Potentially Positive" %></li>
    <% else %>
        <li><%= "Presumed Positive" %></li>
    <% end %>
    <li>Fever Free? <%= @isolation.fever_free ? "Yes" : "No"%></li>
    <li>Earliest Possible End Date: <%= @isolation.end_date || "Not Listed" %></li>
    <li>Overall Status: <%= @isolation.completed ? "Isolation Complete" : "Isolation Incomplete" %></li>
</ul>

<p>The Pingry School</p>
